title: World Vegetarian Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Pizza, International, Organic, Western, Take-out, Bakery
description: Vegetarian cafe opened Sept 2015 serving vegetarian dishes with global flavors for breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Most dishes are vegan or can be made vegan. Offers desserts that are raw, vegan, gluten free, soy free. Beverages include organic fair trade coffee and house-made chai.
